Umm. Which elementary school did I go to?

16
00:01:19,041 --> 00:01:20,249
Umm.

17
00:01:20,250 --> 00:01:21,290
Nope. Can’t remember anything at all.

18
00:01:21,541 --> 00:01:22,540
Nope. Not even my secondary school.

19
00:01:24,666 --> 00:01:25,790
Seven
This doesn’t make sense

20
