Gosh! I’m seeing some terrifying things!

23
00:02:23,833 --> 00:02:24,624
Yup, seems like he’s fine now.

24
00:02:28,416 --> 00:02:31,165
The remnants of poison in your body has been fully purged.

25
00:02:31,583 --> 00:02:33,915
It’s just that the memories from your past have been forgotten for a long period of time.

26
00:02:34,541 --> 00:02:37,665
You need a little something to bring those memories back

27
00:02:39,083 --> 00:02:42,040
As long as you come into contact with objects and people from your past,

28
00:02:42,541 --> 00:02:44,332
