136
00:12:16,083 --> 00:12:17,332
Uhm… What if..

137
00:12:17,333 --> 00:12:18,624
Just in case…

138
00:12:18,666 --> 00:12:20,124
What if it’s a really dire situation,

139
00:12:20,125 --> 00:12:21,540
