146
00:12:48,250 --> 00:12:49,874
Here, I’ve got a pouch.

*Marvellous!*

147
00:12:50,416 --> 00:12:53,457
When you are in absolute danger, open it up and take a look at the items inside.

148
00:12:53,958 --> 00:12:55,207
It might be able to help you.

149
00:13:00,625 --> 00:13:02,165
Heh, heh, heh, heh…

150
00:13:02,166 --> 00:13:04,999
